ast.name: Clearer
ast.comment:
Clearer is a helpful checklist script with a slick interface. Unlike most other to-do apps, Clearer takes the advantage of gestures to give you a completely new experience.

Full feature list:
✔Slick interface (uses accent color)
✔Smooth animations
✔Use gestures to mark tasks as done, add or delete tasks
✔Easy to use
✔Awesome Live Tile

New in V1.1:
✔Everything is now stored in records
✔Task lists
✔You can now rename your tasks/lists
✔Fixed some bugs
